	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Pauca scribo, quoniam iamiam abiturus est hic noster.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Quid <placeName ref="l2">Arovię</placeName> actum, ex vestris legatis cognovisti.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de">Hie hätt üwer schreiben und das zemmenkommen zuͦ <placeName ref="l2">Arow</placeName> sovil bracht, das der handel wider wirt für räth und burger kommen.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de">Die botten sind wol verritten gen <placeName ref="l21">Baden</placeName>; man wirt inen aber nachschryben.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de">Uff hütt sind all min herren, die uß sind, beschriben.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Quid interim sperem, nescio.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de">Die gmein burgerschafft wär guͦt; <foreign xml:lang="la">capita sunt aegra.</foreign></s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de"><foreign xml:lang="la">Putant multi,</foreign> man mögs wol böser, aber nitt beßer machen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Nos nostrum praestamus officium; singulis concionibus declamamus de hac de omnes, accedimus etiam senatum, ut proxime scripsi.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Sed eo redeunt nostri evangelici, ut parum curent illud OS DOMINI LOQUUTUM EST.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Expecto, quid tu per <persName ref="p4191">Apiarium</persName> scribas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Quas hic mitto, heri a <persName ref="p540">Calvino</persName> accepi.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8111">Petri Martyris</persName> literas, apertae cum essent, legi.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><foreign xml:lang="de">Mitt <placeName ref="l167">Genff</placeName> hoff ich wird sich die sach zuuͦ guͦtem zien;</foreign> non ausim scribere, qualiter cum illis agatur; sed ipsi pro sua prudentia pulchre sustinent importunitatem, ne dicant improbitatem hanc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la">Forte de his <persName ref="p540">Calvinus</persName> aliqua; is quasi in signum positus est, cui contradicitur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la">Raptim.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Fratri salutem dicas; non potui illi nunc scribere.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la">Salvi sint tui omnes.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l41">Bernae</placeName>, 28. octobris 1555.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p8018">I[oannes] H[allerus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la">D. <persName ref="p3544">Wolphgango ab Erlach</persName> <placeName ref="l21">Badenam</placeName> proficiscenti omnes scripturae locos exscripsi, et omnia alia argumenta quum ex tuis literis tum aliunde ad hanc rem pertinentia collecta tradidi cum quibusdam etiam locis ex Patribus et iure canonico <persName ref="p8417">Musculi</persName> opera conquisitis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf...:]</note>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri suo charissimo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de">M. <persName ref="p495">Heinrych Bullingern</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587">Zürich</placeName></s>
				</p>
			</div>
